{"tid":2268310,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔成日講有錢就有女?有冇實際個數?","createTime":"2020-11-02T16:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T09:51:35.000Z","uid":249170,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1aba007c2c371b6481bd6287db46c789aef81d38","tid":2268310,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔成日講有錢就有女?<br />\n有冇實際個數?有幾多錢先有女?<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為起碼過億<br />\n因為香港人無論男女<br />\n個個月入40k以上，至少一層5百萬以上既樓揸手，女仔揾錢可能仲會易d<br />\n<br />\n所以人人都咁揾得錢情況下，<br />\n有錢人定義要進一步提高<br />\n<br />\n身家不足5百萬係窮人<br />\n身家千萬頭其實係普通平民<br />\n<br />\n真正有錢人身家係過億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇父幹，唔係做犯法野有冇可能揾到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14a0a20fc464052dfa7e038e81832fc2a8ba07","tid":2268310,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"月入3M,有超過100M物業<br />\n<br />\n利申：32歲就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470e9f636960f1c7d5ab7dfd92c00cffb8b34987","tid":2268310,"uid":243351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae14a0a20fc464052dfa7e038e81832fc2a8ba07","tid":2268310,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"月入3M,有超過100M物業<br />\n<br />\n利申：32歲就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"可摸耳做你隻狗"},{"pid":"32c05863dbe5b2d8139da092b1f1b7256e0baaab","tid":2268310,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，我入去做乜嘢"},{"pid":"870c53af8333b76b8e7e0019dabfbd62e17c8521","tid":2268310,"uid":357591,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1aba007c2c3